dict.owner: SCHICK TECHNOLOGIES - Viewset Item Creator ID

entry.name: Image Instance UID
entry.definition: The Instance UID of the Image that should be displayed in this Viewbox (may be blank).

entry.name: Number
entry.definition: Sequential number representing the order it was created.

entry.name: Order
entry.definition: A number that represents the order in which the series should be taken.

entry.name: Type
entry.definition: A number describing anatomical position for this image. 1 = Upper Left5 = Right Bitewing 2 = Upper Center6 = Lower Left 3 = Upper Right7 = Lower Center 4 = Left Bitewing8 = Lower Right

entry.name: Rect (Left, Top, Width, Height)
entry.definition: A rectangle of coordinates stored as (Left\Top\Width\Height) that describe the position and dimension of the Viewbox. The coordinates are based on a 1024x768 window.

entry.name: Caption Height
entry.definition: Height of the caption text in corrdinates displayed below the ViewBox. This height should be subtracted from the above Rect before displaying and image box.

entry.name: Source
entry.definition: The Acquisition Source for the image box.
